Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,活动室在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在社团活动楼3层最里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3层最里面?
